column27: Mapping and cloning of a resistance gene for Albugo laibachii from the Arabidopsis accession HR-5
column29: RNA was extracted from the leaves of adult HR-5 plants (no pathogen or elicitor treatment) and processed to a cDNA library using the KAPA stranded RNAseq kit, and amplified with barcoding oligos. This library was pooled with others and then captured with the v2 BrRenSeq bait library and then sequenced on the MiSeq.
